data.description:
Don't miss this BEAUTIFULLY designed Abbeyville model featuring a covered rocking chair front porch.
Great Rm w/stone FP, Sunrm leading out to your Screened Porch, Patio, & large, level yard. Kitchen w/stainless appliances, FARM sink w/instant hot water, refrigerator included, granite countertops, custom backsplash. Oversized island w/pendant lights & under cab lighting. Great open floor plan. Owner's suite w/tray ceiling & lg. walk-in closet. Laundry rm w/huge walk-in storage closet. Custom designed closet storage. Drop zone leads to 4' ext. gar. w/utility sink & walk-up attic storage.Tankless water heater. Inground irrigation. AWARD WINNING Carolina Orchards amenities include fitness center, indoor/outdoor pools & hot tubs, 8 lit pickleball cts, 4 lit tennis cts, 2 bocce cts, dog park, grandkids park, full-time activities director, numerous clubs & activities to choose from. Anne Springs Greenway across the street. Come join us in the Orchards. It's a great place to call home.
